text: Muradlı may refer to: * Mahammad Muradli, 2015 World Youth Chess Champion from Azerbaijan * Muradlı, Agsu, a village and municipality in the Agsu Rayon of Azerbaijan * Moradlu District, a district in Meshgin Shahr County, Ardabil Province, Iran * Haçıalmuradlı, a village and municipality in the Imishli Rayon of Azerbaijan
title: Muradlı
